<item>
            <title>[LU-16918] Re-enable less commonly used build configurations</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16918</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Support for --disable-modules was lost a while back. Other less&lt;br/&gt;
frequently used build combinations were also impacted.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The libcfs module cannot be built if modules are not enabled,&lt;br/&gt;
however the header files which contain inline functions and&lt;br/&gt;
#define translations can be used and are needed for compilation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
